{
    "title": "Sourcemod开发环境搭建",
    "date": "2026-06-25",
    "author": "Pure_*",
    "content": [
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "前言" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "SourceMod 是运行在 Source 引擎游戏（如 Left 4 Dead 2、CS:GO、TF2 等）上的服务端插件框架。本文以 Left 4 Dead 2 为例，介绍从零开始搭建 SourceMod 插件开发环境的完整流程，包括专用服务器安装、Metamod / SourceMod 部署、编辑器配置以及插件编译与测试。"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "完成本教程后，你将拥有一台可本地调试的 L4D2 服务器，并能在 VS Code 中编写、编译 SourcePawn 插件。"
            ]
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "环境要求" },
        {
            "type": "table",
            "data": {
                "headers": [
                    "项目",
                    "说明"
                ],
                "rows": [
                    [
                        "操作系统",
                        "Windows 10 / 11（64 位）或 Linux"
                    ],
                    [
                        "代码编辑器",
                        "Visual Studio Code（推荐）/Cursor/或其他代码编辑器"
                    ],
                    [
                        "AI助手",
                        "AI助手可以帮助你完成一些繁琐的代码编写，如DeepSeek（推荐）/Copilot/Claude等"
                    ]
                ]
            }
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "第一步：下载并安装代码编辑器（以VS Code为例）" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "1. 下载安装 Visual Studio Code：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官网下载</a>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/vscode_offical_site.png",
                "alt": "VS Code 官网界面",
                "caption": "图1 VS Code 官网界面"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "2. 下载好安装包后，跟随安装指引完成安装"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "3. 打开扩展市场，搜索并安装 SourcePawn Studio插件"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/sourcepawn_studio_plugin.png",
                "alt": "SourcePawn Studio插件",
                "caption": "图2 SourcePawn Studio插件"
            }
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "第二步：下载Sourcemod基础环境包" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "1. 确认自己需要的Sourcemod版本，一般地，下载自己服务器对应版本的Sourcemod包要更好一点。这里提供两个大版本的下载地址：",
                "\t- <a href=\"https://www.sourcemod.net/downloads.php?branch=stable\" target=\"_blank\">Sourcemod 1.12</a>",
                "\t- <a href=\"https://www.sourcemod.net/downloads.php?branch=1.11-dev\" target=\"_blank\">Sourcemod 1.11</a>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "2. 选择你要下载的环境包，推荐Windows，Windows编写和编译的插件，在Linux服务器上一样生效"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/sourcemod_download.png",
                "alt": "Sourcemod下载界面",
                "caption": "图3 Sourcemod下载界面"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/sourcemod_zip.png",
                "alt": "Sourcemod环境压缩包",
                "caption": "图4 Sourcemod环境压缩包"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "3. 打开压缩包，进入addons文件夹，将sourcemod文件夹解压到你的开发文件夹下，开发文件夹是你认为合适的地方"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/unzip_sourcemod_zip.png",
                "alt": "解压环境包",
                "caption": "图5 解压环境包（这里作者还做了重命名）"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "4. 开发环境准备完毕，下面开始验证环境是否搭建成功"
            ]
        },
        { "type": "header", "level": 2, "data": "第三步：在VSCode中链接Sourcemod" },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "1. 打开VSCode，点击左上角File->Open Folder，选择你刚刚解压的Sourcemod环境包的文件夹，打开后编辑器如下图所示"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/open_sourcemod_folder.png",
                "alt": "打开Sourcemod环境文件夹",
                "caption": "图6 打开Sourcemod环境文件夹"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "2. 在左侧空白区域右键，唤出菜单，选择New Folder，创建一个命名为.vscode的文件夹"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/vscode_new_folder.png",
                "alt": "创建.vscode文件夹",
                "caption": "图7 创建.vscode文件夹"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "3. 在.vscode文件夹上右键，唤出菜单，选择New File，创建一个命名为settings.json的文件"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": {
                "url": "data/tutorials/env_setup/images/vscode_create_settings.png",
                "alt": "创建settings.json文件",
                "caption": "图8 创建settings.json文件"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "4. 在进入sourcemod/scripting/include文件夹，将include文件夹的路径复制到剪贴板"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "5. 将下列代码填写到settings.json文件中"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "data": [
                "{",
                "    \"sourcepawn.includePaths\": [",
                "        \"C:/l4d2server/left4dead2/addons/sourcemod/scripting/include\"  // 粘贴你刚刚复制的路径",
                "    ]",
                "}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": [
                "5. 保存文件，VSCode中链接Sourcemod环境成功"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
